      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-sgr-pro-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      09                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      30                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      rr-sgr-map           to   v-num                  .
